Fenella Woolgar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fenella_Woolgar 0 Fenella Woolgar (born 4 August 1969) is an English actress. She trained at RADA graduating in 1999. She has worked in film with Mike Leigh, Woody Allen, Stephen Frears and Stephen Fry; television – most recently in Harlots for ITV and Hulu; theatre at the Donmar, National, Old Vic and Royal Court and regularly on radio for BBC Radio 4.
